   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3174_0024"/><hi rend="underline" n="1"><date when="1904-08-11">Morgen</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>früh nach 8 Uhr</time> zuzustellen!</hi></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">XVIII Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 7</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3174_0025"/><date when="1904-08-10">Mittwoch</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time>.</dateline><salute rend="left">Mein lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Es hätte mir doch gar zu leid gethan, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs> zu
               verla<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en, ohne Dich ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen zu haben. Ich habe daher meine Abrei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e um einen Tag
               ver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>choben und werde <date when="1904-08-11">morgen, Donner<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date>, gegen
                  <time>Mittag</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03450-1"/>zu Dir<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03450-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1904-08-11" subtype="See"/>.
               </note> hinauskommen.</p><closer>Herzlichen Gruß! <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
